subject: O.M.G.
author: Adriana Jones
full_text: We did a ghost box session at a grave yard tonight, and all I can say is OMG!  This file is way too personal to share online, but OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG!!!!!  There is definitely without a shadow of a doubt.... something out there!   OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG OMG...... lol!
